name: Watercolor Tank
description:
Ever wanted to wear your own piece of artwork? Wanted a shirt so simple, yet an eye catcher at the same time? A shirt that goes with nearly everything? If your answer was yes, then you'll love getting this shirt, it's affordable, yet soft and delicate. You can dress it up or down with just the fewest accessories. This is truly a one-of-a-kind shirt. 

Brand: Sydney Taylor
Material: Cotton
Condition: New. The shirts are made and then sent directly to your door.
Model's Sizes: Small; Height: 5'6 

*Note: This is a one of a kind shirt, and like all watercolor paintings, they can't turn out identical. The shirt will be as similar as possible to the one pictured.*

**Only 10 will be made and sold in the US.**
